to w.commit() which causes the IDs to offset by 1.\r\n\r\nSince RIW.flushAt is set to 51 (w/ the above seed), you can reduce the number of docs to index to 53 and the bug will be exposed (it didn't reproduce w/ N_DOCS=52). I'll try to isolate this bug to a standalone testcase and then run on 3x too.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=shaie","name":"shaie","emailAddress":"serera at gmail dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Shai Erera","active":true},"created":"2011-07-03T06:14:26.478+0000","updated":"2011-07-03T06:14:26.478+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12512410/comment/13059173","id":"13059173","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=shaie","name":"shaie","emailAddress":"serera at gmail dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Shai Erera","active":true},"body":"Ok -- reproduced consistently with -Dtests.seed=2719714750176374101:2498146487036328796. Issue was that test must use LogMergePolicy and not any out-of-order merges.\r\n\r\nCommitted revision 1142385 (3x).\r\nCommitted revision 1142386 (trunk).","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=shaie","name":"shaie","emailAddress":"serera at gmail dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/u